Script Introduction to Data Analysis Lena Janys 2019-10-11 Chapter 1 Organizational Info: This course is an introduction to data analysis using the programming language R The bookdown package can be installed from CRAN or Github: Remember each Rmd file contains one and only one chapter, and a chapter is defined by the first-level heading #. To compile this example to PDF, you need XeLaTeX. You are recommended to install TinyTeX (which includes XeLaTeX): https://yihui.name/tinytex/.
